msgctxt "announce_finesthour_release"
msgid "The long awaited release is finally here! The <c(f5d167)>COMMONWEALTH</c> forces have arrived to the battlefield! It is not only our biggest production to date, but it also adds a <c(f5d167)>whole new level of detail and cinematography to the singleplayer experience</c>.\n\n'Finest Hour' tells the story of the British commonwealth forces in western Europe, the Polish forces in exile, and the German invasion of France and eventual retreat.\n\n 'We shall fight in France, we shall fight on the seas and oceans, we shall fight with growing confidence and growing strength in the air, we shall defend our Island, whatever the cost may be, we shall fight on the beaches, we shall fight on the landing grounds, we shall fight in the fields and in the streets, we shall fight in the hills; <c(f5d167)>we shall never surrender!</c>.'"
msgstr ""
